It is with a heavy heart that I share the news of the passing of my sweet mother-in-law, Boni. She was an amazing woman, full of kindness, love, and warmth. Her unwavering devotion to her family and selflessness will never be forgotten.  Her loss has left a void in our lives that can never be filled. Please keep our family, especially Travis and his sister, who have now lost both parents in such a short span of time, in your thoughts and prayers as we navigate through this difficult time. Rest in peace, Boni. You will be greatly missed but never forgotten.

@travishollman made it home last night to celebrate Ron’s 95th bday.  Ron has lived with us for 6 years and has become part of our family.  Ron you are a shining example of wisdom, kindness, and love. Here's to another year filled with joy and blessings.🎉🎂🥳 #happybirthdayron #familylove #95neverlookedsogood #grateful #histietho

This weekend was bittersweet as we gathered in Oregon to celebrate the incredible life of my late mother in law, Boni. We laughed, we cried, and we reminisced about all the wonderful memories we shared with her. Even though she's no longer with us, her spirit lives on in the love and joy she brought to everyone she knew. Rest in peace, Boni. We love you and miss you dearly. ❤️ #family #love #celebration #memories #oregon #inlovingmemory #restinpeace
Thank you all so much for the birthday wishes!  Here's to another year of making memories with the ones I love ❤️🎉 #birthdayvibes #grateful #blessed #friendsandfamily #celebrationtime
